Though this may seem far , far away , in fact , <COREF ID="0" TYPE="IDENT">Palau</COREF> is geographically the closest to <COREF ID="21" TYPE="IDENT">Taiwan</COREF> of all the countries with which <COREF ID="21" TYPE="IDENT">the ROC</COREF> has formal diplomatic ties .
