Jewels in the Pacific
<COREF ID="19" TYPE="IDENT"><COREF ID="30" TYPE="IDENT">Taiwan</COREF> and <COREF ID="45" TYPE="IDENT">Palau</COREF></COREF> share much more in common in terms of culture and historical position than most people realize .
