Reinvigorating the tourism market
Lin Neng - jong says there are two viable directions to get into the <COREF ID="16" TYPE="IDENT">Palau</COREF> tourism industry .
One is to invest in a tourism - related industry in <COREF ID="16" TYPE="IDENT">Palau</COREF> , the other is to increase the number of <COREF ID="38" TYPE="IDENT">Taiwan</COREF> tourists and extend profit opportunities into <COREF ID="38" TYPE="IDENT">Taiwan <COREF ID="38" TYPE="IDENT">itself</COREF></COREF> .
