In <COREF ID="34" TYPE="IDENT">1997</COREF> , there were more than 70,000 foreign visits to <COREF ID="16" TYPE="IDENT">Palau</COREF> .
Last year the figure was 50,000 .
<COREF ID="38" TYPE="IDENT">Taiwan</COREF> has been , along with Japan , one of the main sources of tourists to <COREF ID="16" TYPE="IDENT">Palau</COREF> .
In <COREF ID="34" TYPE="IDENT">1997</COREF> , the number of Taiwanese visitors peaked at more than 30,000 annually , but now is down to well below 20,000 .
