<COREF ID="7" TYPE="IDENT">James Yeh , general manager of the Sunrise Express Travel Service , which specializes in Pacific Island tours ,</COREF> says that the current trend among travelers in <COREF ID="38" TYPE="IDENT">Taiwan</COREF> is for low group fares with lots of entertainment provided .
