Though <COREF ID="16" TYPE="IDENT">Palau</COREF> is rich in natural attractions , <COREF ID="16" TYPE="IDENT">it</COREF> lacks peripheral tourist facilities like pubs , shopping centers , and gift shops , so naturally <COREF ID="16" TYPE="IDENT">the islands</COREF> are less attractive .
